Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)申し訳ありません｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エルが脱走しました！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But El has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:09.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌｧﾊﾞﾛ･ﾚｵｰﾈ)カイザル！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ぬぅ～！\Nキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボォーン‼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)\Nありがと ムガロちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと\N変わったかもしれないけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have changed a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも\Nムガロちゃんはムガロちゃんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)乗れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)\Nアザゼル お前の力を貸してくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔を助けたいのだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to save the demons, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力してくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:39.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)\N闘技場から脱走した者たちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The fugitives from the arena
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も逃走中です｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王都の外に逃げ出せぬよう\N厳重に包囲網を張っております｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've set a perimeter around the capital\Nto ensure they do not escape the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who helped them escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)\N逃走に手を貸したという男➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファバロ･レオーネに違いない｡\N(隊長)おそらくは｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was assuredly Favaro Leone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will handle him with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まとめて処理いたします｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And also regarding the red dragon,\Nwe will be sure to slay it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:58.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い竜に関しても\N次こそは必ず始末します｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらのいる所に\N赤い竜は幾度となく現れました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The red dragon has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,many times wherever that bunch\Nis involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely happen upon the dragon\Nif we pursue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追えば いずれ出会えましょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill it on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけしだい殺せ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something I should know\Nabout the red dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い竜に何か？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もない｡ 行け｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let them escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:39.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)なぜ 逃がしたのです！\N(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)申し訳ございません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)あなたがいながら\Nなんたる失態！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you must understand what it\Nmeans for us to lose El at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 エルを失うことの意味が\N分からないわけではないでしょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We will send a search party immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに捜索いたします｡\N(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)当然です｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously. We must get El back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず エルを取り戻すのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)私が行きます｡\N(２人)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)控えなさい！\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)あの子が 人に捕まれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be killed if he's ever captured\Nby the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺されます｡\N黙って見過ごすなどできません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot stand by and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You would only get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが行っても\N足手まといになるだけです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my insolence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)お言葉ながら\Nエルに信用されていない➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but leaving this matter to those\Nwho are not trusted by El
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなた方に任せて\Nなんとかなるとは思えません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is not very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go alone if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人でも 私は行きます｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)待ちなさい ジャンヌ！\N(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)私にお任せを｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カラン カラン…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:43.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)ひどいことしますねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:46.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタ 大丈夫かな？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)分からねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Rita is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(ﾘﾀ)あんたたち まさか それ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your idea of a disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変装してるつもり？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リタだ！\N(ﾘﾀ)そうよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same\Nand lose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz there are lots of roads to go\NAnd the path suddenly seems rougher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna walk straight ahead\NKnock down another dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Most broke before they ever came true
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the way you think it\NTo a yielding heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the future, hope,\Ndespair and worry all look all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that you'll turn down the truth\Nthat lied to you that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were prepared for it all.\NYou go your way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん｡\N≪(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)アザゼルは どこ行った？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Azazel go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:49.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らねぇ｡ 朝から見てねぇな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea. Haven't seen him since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)今度は\N爆発しないだろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This one won't explode, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあな｡\Nさあなって お前！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫師匠！\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)ただいま｡\N生きてたんですね 師匠！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが 師匠は無敵です｡\Nおう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I can't believe the luck\Nyou seem to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:09.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめぇも\N悪運だけは強ぇみてぇだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ？ なんだ？ その顔｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ…｡\Nちょっ… お前➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you okay with me,\Nbut you blush with Kaisar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は大丈夫なのに なんで\Nカイザルに 顔赤くしてんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)なんだクワァ\Nこの感じ 久しぶりですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bringing back some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ああ～ 酒が飲みてぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)その少年は？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ん？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌの息子だ｡\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ジャンヌ様は？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Jeanne's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Jeanne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)まだ 神の国だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still in the land of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)私はカイザル･リドフｧルド｡\N君のお母さんの元部下だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kaisar Lidfard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to serve your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's gotten angsty\Nwhile they were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し見ないうちに\N生意気になったわね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)私たちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to determine\Nwhat King Charioce is trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオス王が このあと\N何をしようとしているのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを見極めたいと考えている｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先の戦いで 王が使用した兵器➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The weapon the king used\Nin the last battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの破壊力は危険すぎる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,its power is far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王の意思しだいでは\N１０年前と変わらぬ危機が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If the king so wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the world could be put in the same danger\Nit was in ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界に訪れるかもしれない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｴﾙ)あれさえなければ\N人を正しい道に戻すことができる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for that weapon, humanity\Ncould be guided back to the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｴﾙ)僕の力ならできる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it with my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ？ このガキ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに あの兵器を封印できれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. If that weapon can be stripped of its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王の真意がどうであれ\N破壊は防げるだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we could prevent destruction\Nno matter what the king's intentions are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし どうやって？\N腕輪よ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 腕輪？\N私 見た➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the king control the black thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王様が\Nあの黒いやつを動かすところを｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was reacting to his bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの腕輪に あれは反応してた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その腕輪を奪う！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We will steal this bracelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugaro, if you break your promise to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nムガロ 俺との約束を破ったら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｴﾙ)分かってるよ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we should gather intel for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)\Nとにかく 今は情報を集めよう｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオス王による強大な危機が\N近づいているのなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If King Charioce is putting the world\Nin danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々で それを防ごう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then we must stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 力を貸してくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We need all of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry I allowed this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)私が付いていながら\Nすまなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Both for letting them escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がしたこともだが 無責任に\Nエルの力を解放したこともだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and also for the part I played\Nin releasing El's power irresponsibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…｡ 我々は性急だった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We were rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エルの力に目がくらみ\Nその力を使いこなすための➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We were blinded by El's powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and we neglected the spiritual growth\Nhe needed to use it responsibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の成長を\Nおろそかにしてしまった｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 信じてくれ｡\N恩人であるエルを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want to lose El.\NI owe him my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:01.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も失いたくない｡\N下界から すぐにでも連れ戻し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to bring him back from\Nthe surface world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたのもとで\N生活させたいと願っている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so the two of you can be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So please leave his search to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 捜索は私に任せてくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)分かりました｡\Nあっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had faith that you would not let me die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:59.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたなら\N助けてくれると信じていました｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま一緒に下界へ降りて\Nエルを捜してください｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me to the surface\Nand help me find El.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは無理だ｡ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの命を\N私たち親子は助けました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My son and I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は あなたが\N私たち親子のために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it is your turn to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力を貸してください｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ソフィエル様 お願いします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sofiel, I beseech you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下界で そなたは追われる身だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a fugitive in the surface world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you vow to me that you will not do\Nanything that would attract danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危険な行動を勝手にせぬこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを誓えるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誓います｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I vow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ… これでは\N私も バッカスと変わらんな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this means I am no different\Nfrom Bacchus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～\Nよし こんなもんかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わあ～！\Nほんとの悪魔みたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I look like a real demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm off to gather some intel, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 情報収集に行ってくる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ちょっと！ 待ちなさい！\Nふふふっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw Nina skipping out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ニーナ嬢が\N元気に飛び出していったが…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She basically went out to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)遊びに行っちゃったわ｡\Nあいつは気楽でいいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be so carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)あんた\Nちょっと ついていきなさいよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？ なんで俺が｡\N(ﾘﾀ)師匠なんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're her master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ねぇだろ｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)行ってこい ボンバーヘｯド｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that gotta do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go, Bomber Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)お嬢さんは\N何に巻き込まれるクワァ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what she might\Nget herself into.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分クワァりませんクワァらね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)任せたぞ ファバロ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Favaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ～！ なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…｡\Nドサッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしている？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ いや あの… う～ん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は悪魔だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What business does a demon have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔が なんの用だ？\Nえ… え～っと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… その墓は 誰の墓だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose grave is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my mother's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の母の墓だ｡\Nえっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ驚く？\Nお… 驚いていない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a commoner who became\Nthe king's concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平民でありながら 王の妾となり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A poor woman who was discarded\Nas soon as she was with child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私をはらんだ途端に捨てられた\Nただの哀れな女だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:23.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に流れる王の血筋だけが\Nこの女の生きる希望だった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the royal blood\Nflowing through my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,gave her hope in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She dreamed even in poverty that one day\Nshe would be invited to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貧しい生活のなかでも いつか\N王室に迎えられる日が来ると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:32.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢見ていたが…｡\Nそれが かなうことはなく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was killed by Bahamut's fire\Nbefore that day could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートの火で\Nあっけなく死んでしまった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was killed\Nby Bahamut's fireballs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:41.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のお父さんも\Nバハムートの火の玉に… あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 皮肉なことに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But ironically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it was because of Bahamut\Nthat I was welcomed to the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:48.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのバハムートの一件により\N私は王室に迎えられ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,母に授けられた\Nクリスという名から➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was given the new name of\NCharioce XVII to replace Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオス１７世へと変わった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the one my mother had given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a demon who lives in the slums,\Nare you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前\Nスラムに住む悪魔なのだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ あっ… はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スラムには\N一度 行ってみたかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to visit the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect. Could you take me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょうどいい\N案内してくれないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take you? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案内？ はい…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely knows it's me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(心の声)\N≪絶対にバレてるよね？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He said I was a demon just now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪さっきは\N悪魔って言ったけど…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an interesting carving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い彫刻だな｡ これをもらうよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 大丈夫？\Nかまわん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 顔がバレちゃうんじゃ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't you be recognized?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 次へ行こう｡\Nあっ… はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)行ったぞ！ 戻れ 戻れ！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 頑張れ 頑張れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get back on defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは 何をしている？\Nえっ？ 分かんない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I think they're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遊んでるんじゃない？\N遊びか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい？\N(子供たち)ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 痛てっ！\N(子供たち)あっ！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was awesome!\N-Can you show me how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:31.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった～！\N(子供)一緒にやろうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も来い！\Nえっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)おねえちゃんも やろうよ！\N(子供)早く 早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on, miss!\N-Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)早く！\Nじゃあ 私も｡ いくぞ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って… ぐえっ！ ひゃあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パリン\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)えっ 何？ 何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:08.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(一同)わあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)行ったぞ！\N(子供)またやろうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, pass it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:23.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)よっしゃ いけ！\N頭のまで取っていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it's okay to take off\Nyour turban too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か\N都合の悪いことでもあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 私 あなたに\N聞きたいことが いっぱいある…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many things\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左上の壁穴を見ろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up and to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)よし！ くそっ もう一回！\N(子供)おい 何やってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちもだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)貸してよ～｡\N(子供)いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたを監視してるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they watching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まくぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we lost them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:17.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとか まけたか｡\Nたぶんね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was reacting to his bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あの腕輪に あれは反応してた))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:39.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 あなたに聞きたいことがある｡\Nなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:46.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは王様で 悪魔にも神にも\N嫌われることを いっぱいしている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've done a lot of things to make\Nthe demons and the gods hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're Chris,\Nyou're so nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに クリスのときは\N私に優しくしたり 踊ったり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You dance with me and you smile at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:54.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔の子供たちにも\N笑顔を向ける｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know which one is the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には どちらの顔が\Nあなたの本心なのか分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what's really inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は知りたい\Nあなたの本当の心を！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をもってしても➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I must achieve\Nat all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,達成しなければ\Nならないことがある｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot tell you what that is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:20.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが なんなのか\N今は答えられない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 全ては\Nそのためだけに必要なことを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say that everything I've done as king
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was necessary for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王として選択してきた｡\Nその結果が 今のありさまだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罪悪感などというものは\Nとうに捨てている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long since abandoned\Nany feelings of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:42.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の覚悟を己に問うためだけに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I only answer to my own convictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,哀れな母の墓へと参っている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as I visit the grave of my poor mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not once had my convictions wavered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:52.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで一度たりとも\Nその覚悟が揺らぐことはなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ お前のことだけは\N割り切ることができなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until you came into my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I never met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前さえ現れなければ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまでどおり\N王として生きていけた！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have lived my life as king\Nwithout a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなのに…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had never met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前とさえ出会わなければ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you want to become a scary king,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが なんで\N怖い王様になろうとするのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 私は あなたのことを…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how I feel about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが抱えているものを\N一緒に背負いたい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you with whatever\Nyou're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バシャーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぷはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned how to transform\Nwhenever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自由に\N変身できるようになっちゃった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:41.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キスしたからかなぁ？ ふふふっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I see you next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は いつ会える？\N分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やだ！\N今度だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Next time.\N-When is next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度って いつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつ？ いつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は今度だ｡\Nはい…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time is next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the next time we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:10.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 次 お前と会えたなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず\N私のなすべきことを伝えよう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you\Nwhat I am trying to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 絶対だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Promise?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わあ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は 私から会いに行く｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll go to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう行け｡\Nうん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As horrible as you are\NI can't help but love you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while I waited\NThat is all I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ephemeral lovers, both flawed and missing pieces\NWe have finally become one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in this miniature garden at the edge of sorrow\NCan you hear my heart speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I may no longer feel\Nthat I want to go back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are feelings, feelings, feelings\NI can only feel now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:23:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to run away with you, dancing\Njust like in a fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it will only be this once, darling\NI am on the same ark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the red dragon had him\Nunder its spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:42.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり\N赤い竜に惑わされていたか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Anatae's Kaisar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven's Jeanne!\NHow is it over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!\NHeaven's Jeanne here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very sparkly!\NIt's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Rage of Bahamut:\NVirgin Soul, "Invictus."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne, could you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,BAHA SOUL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Baha Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time too, okay?
